      <title>大众汽车因保时捷电动汽车电池引发船舶火灾而面临两起诉讼</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-05/volkswagen-faces-lawsuits-over-claim-porsche-ev-battery-sparked-ship-fire</link>
      <description><![CDATA[大众汽车公司在德国面临两起诉讼，据称是保时捷电动汽车的电池引发了 2022 年一艘大型货船的火灾，最终导致船上数千辆汽车沉没。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-05/volkswagen-faces-lawsuits-over-claim-porsche-ev-battery-sparked-ship-fire</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 05 Mar 2024 08:08:02 GMT</pubDate>
